programme.desc: Ben Weiland isn't your typical surfer. While most wave-seekers salivate over the idea of traveling to tropical reefs in equatorial climates, Weiland found his passion in hunting a different kind of surf. In the process, he's uncovered new waves and redefined surf exploration.
